                <a href="https://github.com/Birat-Poudel/Natural-Language-Processing-Projects" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:text-green-700 dark:hover:text-green-300 font-medium text-sm transition-colors group">
