                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">Fundamental ML Projects</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">● Titanic Survival Prediction (Decision Tree Classifier)</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">● Breast Cancer Classification (Logistic Regression)</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">● Automobile Price Prediction (Linear, Ridge, and Lasso Regression)</p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">● Supermarket Sales Prediction (XGBoost Regressor)</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/Birat-Poudel/Machine-Learning" class="inline-flex items-center text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:text-green-700 dark:hover:text-green-300 font-medium text-sm transition-colors group">
